    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Heater and Defroster</title>
        <para>The heater and environmental controls are located on the right wing dash panel directly below the right
            wing switch panel. The heater controls are a cable type activation switch. They connect to the main heater
            assembly in the step well area.
        </para>
